text: Chichester Central is an electoral ward of Chichester District, West Sussex, England and returns one member to sit on Chichester District Council. Following a district boundary review, Chichester Central was created from the neighbouring wards of Chichester (East, North and South) in 2019. ==Councillor== {| class="wikitable" |- !colspan="2"|Year!!Member!!Party |- |style="background-color: " | |2019 |Martyn Bell ||Conservative |} ==Election results== ==References== ==External links== * Chichester District Council * Election Maps Category:Wards of Chichester District
